A little good news. The Sumatran rhinoceros are critically endangered, with perhaps a total of 80 adults dwelling in the forests of Sumatra. They are very hard to find.

Now a baby rhino has been born in Way-Kambas-Nationalpark! The first in a long time. 

#Climate #nature
